data\";s:11:\"highlighted\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35:\"https://community.1and1.com/?p=9776\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:321:\"<p>Learn about new features and enhancements in your 1&#038;1 Control Panel.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com/1and1-control-panel-whats-new/\">1&#038;1 Control Panel: What&#8217;s new?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com\">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Philipp Bellmann\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15098:\"<p>Learn about new features and enhancements in your 1&amp;1 Control Panel.</p>\n<h2>May / April 2017</h2>\n<p>In the last few weeks we added new functions to the E-mail, Office 365 and Domains sections and took the opportunity to fix a few small bugs.</p>\n<h3>Managing external domains with 1&amp;1</h3>\n<p>You can manage external domains (domains registered with another provider) with 1&amp;1 by going to <strong>Domains</strong> &gt; <a href=\"https://my.1and1.com/domains\">Set up external domain</a>. This is how it works:</p>\n<a href=\"https://my.1and1.com/domains\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9859 size-full\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-panel-external-domain-setup.png\" alt=\"control-panel-external-domain-setup\" width=\"2491\" height=\"1130\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-panel-external-domain-setup.png 2491w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-panel-external-domain-setup-300x136.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-panel-external-domain-setup-768x348.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-panel-external-domain-setup-1024x465.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2491px) 100vw, 2491px\" /></a>\n<ul>\n<li>Enter an external domain</li>\n<li>Choose a 1&amp;1 contract (if you have multiple contracts with 1&amp;1)</li>\n<li>Choose a name server (1&amp;1 or other provider)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For a full walkthrough and additional information, please visit 1&amp;1 Help: <a href=\"http://help.1and1.com/domains-c36931/transfer-domains-c79823/to-1and1-c37567/set-up-an-external-domain-with-1and1-a594802.html\" target=\"_blank\">Set Up an External Domain with 1&amp;1</a></p>\n<h3>Activate SSL certificates more easily</h3>\n<p>SSL certificates provide secure, encrypted data transfer and protect your visitors&#8217; important data. That builds trust. SSL is also an important ranking factor used by Google.</p>\n<p>To make using SSL with 1&amp;1 as easy as possible, we added the option to activate your SSL certificates on the following pages in the 1&amp;1 Control Panel:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://my.1and1.com/websitecheck\" target=\"_blank\">1&amp;1 Website Checker</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://my.1and1.com/security-overview\" target=\"_blank\">Security overview</a></li>\n</ul>\n<a href=\"https://my.1and1.com/security-overview\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9856 size-full\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/security-ssl-activate-free.png\" alt=\"security-ssl-activate-free\" width=\"2048\" height=\"916\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/security-ssl-activate-free.png 2048w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/security-ssl-activate-free-300x134.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/security-ssl-activate-free-768x344.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/security-ssl-activate-free-1024x458.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" /></a>\n<ul>\n<li>On the details page of your domain. <strong>Domains</strong> &gt; <strong>Actions</strong> &gt; <a href=\"https://my.1and1.com/domains\" target=\"_blank\">Show details</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Microsoft Office 365</h3>\n<p>The new <a href=\"https://my.1and1.com/office365-overview\" target=\"_blank\">Office 365</a> section contains the following functions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Manage users</strong>: Create users for Microsoft Office 365 and manage their licenses.</li>\n<li><strong>Use Office 365 in a browser</strong>: Open your apps directly in a browser with no installation necessary.</li>\n<li><strong>Install Office 365</strong>: Download apps for your mobile devices (iOS, Android, Windows Phone), for a Windows PC or for a Mac.</li>\n</ul>\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-9855 aligncenter\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/office-365-all-devices.png\" alt=\"office-365-all-devices\" width=\"960\" height=\"408\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/office-365-all-devices.png 960w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/office-365-all-devices-300x128.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/office-365-all-devices-768x326.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" />\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Easy setup</strong>: We guide you through a few necessary steps to set up your account and install your apps. You can find instructions, tips and answers to frequently asked questions on our <a href=\"https://www.1and1.com/help/office365/\">Office 365 help</a> site.</li>\n<li><strong>1&amp;1 Mail &amp; Office Setup Service</strong>: If you would like assistance, we will help you set up Microsoft Office 365 and your 1&amp;1 domain and import your e-mails, contacts and calendar entries.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"promo-button\" href=\"https://my.1and1.com/office365-overview\">Manage Microsoft Office 365 in 1&amp;1 Control Panel</a></p>\n<h3>1&amp;1 rankingCoach</h3>\n<p>1&amp;1 rankingCoach helps you optimize your website to get a better ranking in search engines.</p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Website analysis</strong>: Identify positive aspects of your website as well as possible weaknesses.</li>\n</ul>\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9852\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/rankingcoach-us.png\" alt=\"rankingcoach-us\" width=\"639\" height=\"343\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/rankingcoach-us.png 960w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/rankingcoach-us-300x161.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/rankingcoach-us-768x412.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, 639px\" />\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>On-page optimization</strong>: Optimize all relevant settings and content on your website step by step.</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Evaluation and monitoring</strong>: Track and compare the success of your optimizations.</li>\n</ul>\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9853\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/rankingcoach-optimization-us.png\" alt=\"rankingcoach-optimization-us\" width=\"630\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/rankingcoach-optimization-us.png 960w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/rankingcoach-optimization-us-300x161.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/rankingcoach-optimization-us-768x412.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\" />\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Support for all major Websites / CMSs:</strong> WordPress, Joomla!, Magento, 1&amp;1 MyWebsite and many other CMSs.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"promo-button\" href=\"https://www.1and1.com/improve-website-ranking\" target=\"_blank\">Analyse your website with 1&amp;1 rankingCoach</a></p>\n<h2>March 2017</h2>\n<h3>Set up and connect domains</h3>\n<p>Sometimes a simple, clear list is the best way to quickly make a selection. That&#8217;s why we&#8217;ve built the <strong>Domains</strong> &gt; <strong>Actions</strong> &gt; <a href=\"https://my.1and1.com/connect-domain/\" target=\"_blank\">Adjust Destination</a> section from scratch and removed all the elements that could distract you from your goal. Now it is even easier to set up your domain.</p>\n<img class=\"alignright wp-image-9780 size-full\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-connect-domain-en-us-Kopie.png\" alt=\"control-center-connect-domain-en-us\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1377\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-connect-domain-en-us-Kopie.png 2048w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-connect-domain-en-us-Kopie-300x202.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-connect-domain-en-us-Kopie-768x516.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-connect-domain-en-us-Kopie-1024x689.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" />\n<p>Connect your domain to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Websites on your webspace at 1&amp;1</li>\n<li>Websites with other providers</li>\n<li>Social media sites (Facebook, Twitter, Google+, Instagram, YouTube, LinkedIn, Pinterest, Xing)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Or set up domain forwarding, an E-Mail Adress and advanced DNS settings.</p>\n<h3>Export Domains to Excel, CSV, XML and JSON</h3>\n<p>Easily <a href=\"https://my.1and1.com/create-domain-export\" target=\"_blank\">export an overview of your domains</a> as an Excel, XML, CSV or JSON file from the Domains section. Using this export file, you can comfortably process important information about your domain in a tool of your choice.</p>\n<img class=\"alignright wp-image-9781 size-full\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-domains-export-en-us.png\" alt=\"control-center-domains-export-en-us\" width=\"2048\" height=\"2214\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-domains-export-en-us.png 2048w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-domains-export-en-us-278x300.png 278w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-domains-export-en-us-768x830.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-domains-export-en-us-947x1024.png 947w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" />\n<p>Features:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Export filters: filter by domain status, type or contract</li>\n<li>Export modifications: the following information can be exported: domain name, TLD, contract, status, mode of use, authorization code, SSL certificate, number of sub-domains and more.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>New functions in the Domains section</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Resetting DNS settings/mode of use</strong>: reset your DNS settings and the mode of use for your domain under <em>Domain</em> &gt; <em>Details</em> &gt; <em>Domain Settings</em> with just two clicks.<br />\nIn the Domain Reset section, you will find information about the mode of use, the current settings for your domain and the effects that the reset will have on your domain.<br />\nIn case of problems, you can easily and securely restart your domain using the 1&amp;1 default settings.</li>\n<li><strong>Transfers</strong>: You can transfer domains between various contracts within a customer number under Domain &gt; Details &gt; Transfer &amp; Extension.</li>\n<li><strong>Filter</strong>: You can now filter domains by phases or transfer types under Domains &gt; Filter:\n<ul>\n<li>outgoing transfers</li>\n<li>incoming transfers</li>\n<li>pre-registrations.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"promo-button\" href=\"https://my.1and1.com/domains\">Manage Domains in 1&amp;1 Control Panel</a></p>\n<h3>List Local</h3>\n<p>If you use 1&amp;1 ListLocal, you can now access your product more easily. While it was only displayed in the contract in which you ordered it in the past, it is now available in all contracts.</p>\n<h3>Search Community Articles from your 1&amp;1 Control Panel</h3>\n<p>Searching 1&amp;1 Control Center&#8217;s main menu now also displays relevant results from our web hosting and server community. You will find tutorials, event reports and information about WordPress, performance optimization, PHP, SEO, SSL, Cloud Server, Docker and network issues like load balancing here.</p>\n<img class=\"alignright wp-image-9782 size-full\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-search-communities-en-us.png\" alt=\"control-center-search-communities-en-us\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1391\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-search-communities-en-us.png 2048w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-search-communities-en-us-300x204.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-search-communities-en-us-768x522.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-search-communities-en-us-1024x696.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" />\n<p>Instead of incredibly long phrases and multi-clause sentences, with us, you can read simple, well-researched articles that are easy to understand and comprehensive.<br />\nVisit us at: <a href=\"https://community.1and1.com\">1&amp;1 Web Hosting Community</a> / <a href=\"https://hosting.1und1.de/cloud-community\">1&amp;1 Cloud Community</a></p>\n<h3>Contract information: New Design</h3>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://my.1and1.com/contract-details\">contract details</a> are now being presented in clean Responsive Design for improved display on desktops, smartphones and tablets.</p>\n<img class=\"alignright wp-image-9783 size-full\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-contract-en-us.png\" alt=\"control-center-contract-en-us\" width=\"2048\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-contract-en-us.png 2048w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-contract-en-us-300x141.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-contract-en-us-768x360.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/control-center-contract-en-us-1024x480.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" />\n<p>Important functions:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Displaying the contract name, number, period</li>\n<li>Accessing details about your products, such as: inclusive domains, e-mail accounts, web spaces, traffic, FTP logins, PHP, online marketing and more</li>\n<li>Managing products: move from the service overview to access the settings page for your products</li>\n<li>Terminating the contract or contract components</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Next Level Hosting:</h3>\n<p>Next Level Hosting from 1&amp;1 provides you with flexible performance that grows to meet your requirements.<br />\nIn the 1&amp;1 Control Panel, you can check the capacity utilization of your websites and applications (CMS) in the <a href=\"https://my.1and1.com/performance-level\">Performance Level</a> section. With increased capacity needs, you can flexibly increase RAM, MEMORY LIMIT and PROCESSES for a direct performance boost without contractual obligations.</p>\n<h3>Help and Support</h3>\n<p>If you are solving a problem with one of our support employees, you probably have your hands full and do not have time to make notes. For that reason, we will summarize the most important information and solutions for you after a call to our support team.</p>\n<p>You will receive this summary automatically by e-mail and, as of now for many issues, in a clear pop-up during your next login to the 1&amp;1 Control Panel as well.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com/1and1-control-panel-whats-new/\">1&#038;1 Control Panel: What&#8217;s new?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com\">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://community.1and1.com/1and1-control-panel-whats-new/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"36\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"WordPress 4.8: The 5 most important innovations + developer features\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-8/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-8/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 09 Jun 2017 06:36:46 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Information\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Release Notes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Web Hosting\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"What\'s new\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35:\"https://community.1and1.com/?p=9820\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:381:\"<p>WordPress 4.8 makes everyday tasks easier with new widgets for videos, pictures and text as well as easy editing of links.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-8/\">WordPress 4.8: The 5 most important innovations + developer features</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com\">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Philipp Bellmann\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6853:\"<p>WordPress 4.8 &#8220;Evans&#8221; (<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/download/\" target=\"_blank\">download</a>) makes everyday tasks easier with new widgets for videos, pictures and text as well as improved editing of links.</p>\n<h2>Features for content creators</h2>\n<p>If you simply want to tell a great story without having to worry about things like PHP, HTML or CSS, these features are for you:</p>\n<h3>1. Editing links has become much easier</h3>\n<p>Adding text to an existing link should always be simple. This is why WordPress 4.8 clearly highlights when you edit the link text. So you always know exactly whether you are creating regular text or link text.</p>\n<iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/220614341?title=0&amp;amp;byline=0\" width=\"640\" height=\"180\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\n<p><strong>Tip</strong>: Once you have finished your link text, just press the right-arrow key on your keyboard to continue with regular text.</p>\n<h3>2. Image widget</h3>\n<p>With the new image widget it is easy to add a profile image or any other image to your site in the footer or sidebar. In the Customizer, you can preview your changes, drag and drop your image, and see it appear automatically.</p>\n<iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/220623189?title=0&amp;amp;byline=0\" width=\"640\" height=\"363\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\n<p>Click <em>Customizer</em> &gt; <em>Widgets</em> &gt; <em>Add Widget</em> and add an image widget to your site.</p>\n<h3>3. Video widget</h3>\n<p>Many successful websites use video to inspire us with engaging content. In WordPress 4.8, you can easily place a video in the widget area of your page with support for videos from your media library and external videos from YouTube, Vimeo and other services via embedded URLs.</p>\n<img class=\"size-large wp-image-9823 aligncenter\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wp-4-8-video-widget-customizer-hl-1024x498.png\" alt=\"wp-4-8-video-widget-customizer-hl\" width=\"1024\" height=\"498\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wp-4-8-video-widget-customizer-hl-1024x498.png 1024w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wp-4-8-video-widget-customizer-hl-300x146.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wp-4-8-video-widget-customizer-hl-768x374.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />\n<p>Add a video to your sidebar or footer: Click <em>Customizer</em> &gt; <em>Widgets</em> &gt; <em>Add Widget</em> &gt; <em>Video</em>.</p>\n<h3>4. Audio widget</h3>\n<p>For podcasters and musicians: Upload your latest song or podcast to the media library and include a compact audio player as a widget in your sidebar or footer.Tip: External songs can be embedded via URLs.</p>\n<img class=\" wp-image-9822 aligncenter\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wp-4-8-audio-widget-customizer-hl.png\" alt=\"wp-4-8-audio-widget-customizer-hl\" width=\"307\" height=\"97\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wp-4-8-audio-widget-customizer-hl.png 529w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wp-4-8-audio-widget-customizer-hl-300x95.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 307px) 100vw, 307px\" />\n<p>To add an audio widget, click <em>Customizer</em> &gt; <em>Widgets</em> &gt; <em>Add Widget</em> &gt; <em>Audio.</em></p>\n<h3>5. Rich text widget</h3>\n<p>The text widget now uses the visual editor. This makes it easy to create lists and links or to emphasize your text in bold or italic. No HTML skills are required!</p>\n<img class=\"size-large wp-image-9825 aligncenter\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wp-4-8-text-widget-customizer-hl-1024x498.png\" alt=\"wp-4-8-text-widget-customizer-hl\" width=\"1024\" height=\"498\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wp-4-8-text-widget-customizer-hl-1024x498.png 1024w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wp-4-8-text-widget-customizer-hl-300x146.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/wp-4-8-text-widget-customizer-hl-768x374.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />\n<p>Click <em>Customizer</em> &gt; <em>Widgets</em> &gt; <em>Add Widget</em> &gt; <em> Text</em></p>\n<hr />\n<h2>Features for developers</h2>\n<p>For developers, WordPress 4.8 brings these innovations (Source: <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/\">wordpress.org</a>):</p>\n<h3>More Accessible Admin Panel Headings</h3>\n<p>New CSS rules mean extraneous content (like “Add New” links) no longer need to be included in admin-area headings. These panel headings improve the experience for people using assistive technologies.</p>\n<h3>Removal of Core Support for WMV and WMA Files</h3>\n<p>As fewer and fewer browsers support Silverlight, file formats which require the Silverlight plugin are being removed from core support. These files will still display as a download link but will no longer be embedded automatically.</p>\n<h3>Multisite Updates</h3>\n<p>New capabilities have been introduced to 4.8 geared towards removing calls to is_super_admin(). Additionally, new hooks and tweaks for more granular control of site and user counts per network have been added.</p>\n<h3>Text-Editor JavaScript API</h3>\n<p>With the addition of TinyMCE to the text widget in 4.8 comes a new JavaScript API for instantiating the editor after page load. This can be used to add an editor instance to any text area, and customize it with buttons and functions. Great for plugin authors!</p>\n<h3>Media Widgets API</h3>\n<p>The introduction of a new base media widget REST API schema to 4.8 opens up possibilities for even more media widgets (like galleries or playlists) in the future. The three new media widgets are powered by a shared base class that covers most of the interactions with the media modal. That class also makes it easier to create new media widgets and paves the way for more to come.</p>\n<h3>Customizer Width Variable</h3>\n<p>Rejoice! New responsive breakpoints have been added to the customizer sidebar to make it wider on high-resolution screens. Customizer controls should use percentage-based widths instead of pixels.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2>WordPress 4.8 update stuck in maintenance mode? There is a simple solution</h2>\n<p>If you update to 4.8 manually and the update process fails at some point, leaving your WordPress website stuck in maintenance mode, there is a simple solution: <a href=\"https://community.1and1.com/how-to-disable-wordpress-maintenance-mode/\">How to disable WordPress maintenance mode after a failed update</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-8/\">WordPress 4.8: The 5 most important innovations + developer features</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://community.1and1.com\">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:47:\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-8/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"ti