xplicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2956:\"<p>WordPress receives additional security improvements with WordPress 4.7.3 This is a <strong>security release</strong> that includes fixes for critical vulnerabilities and improvements for WordPress 4.7.2 and lower and is recommended for all WordPress users.</p>\n<p>As always, <strong>Managed WordPress websites will be updated by 1&amp;1 automatically.</strong> If you have installed WordPress yourself or use a standard installation from the 1&amp;1 App Center, you can update to 4.7.3 from your WordPress <strong>Dashboard.</strong><strong>  </strong>Select<strong> </strong><strong>Updates</strong> and click <strong>Update Now</strong>.</p>\n<p>If you prefer to update manually, you can <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/download/\" target=\"_blank\">download WordPress 4.7.3 here</a>.</p>\n<h2>What&#8217;s new in WordPress 4.7.3?</h2>\n<p>For a complete list of all bug fixes and improvements please see the official <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress 4.7.3 release notes</a>.</p>\n<h3>You might also like</h3>\n<div class=\"column-33\">\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9615 size-full\" src=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/2017-preview-vi-customizer.png\" width=\"2780\" height=\"1604\" srcset=\"https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/2017-preview-vi-customizer.png 2780w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/2017-preview-vi-customizer-300x173.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/2017-preview-vi-customizer-768x443.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/2017-preview-vi-customizer-1024x591.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2780px) 100vw, 2780px\" />\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://community.1and1.com/wordpress-4-7/\">WordPress 4.7 reviewed</a><br />\n</p></div><div class=\